Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是因為你亂竄才會迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我走開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.97,0:01:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是女孩子正確的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.43,0:01:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這島上的女孩子都想和我一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.31,0:01:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又老是無防備並且都感覺不到羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.34,0:01:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.61,0:01:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之給我走開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:34.96,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要迷惑他…繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.02,0:03:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　炸豬排
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　剛才那麼突然真是嚇死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.74,0:03:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吃一驚的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是　忽然把你打飛真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概馬上就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢　不習慣被他人看到裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是　本來正常就該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.28,0:04:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼很受女生青睞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡時候被盯著看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有想摸我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是災難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜在女生中很受歡迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有男子氣概
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子氣概
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:46.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉　不是那奇怪的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了　從職業上也是沒辦法的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了　公子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話來我們的工作現場來幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.32,0:05:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　不是都說了別再偷偷摸摸跟蹤我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說我可認真的愛著姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了別說那麼噁心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的工作公子也會來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人　真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真來現場不會如此簡單罷休的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.57,0:05:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要命的話明天給我乖乖的呆在家裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是做的過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事　沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.04,0:06:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷路?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後途中見到凜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我帶路了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長了個包　怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.31,0:06:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天作為回禮要去幫凜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎　受到幫助了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天我也早起好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:45.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴就算了　慢慢的睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我擅自決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴也有家事要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那種事情早點起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆利落地做完就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.96,0:06:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:06:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早睡就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動～了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　我家的人都不知道好好品嘗味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴去拿西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個很忙的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天行人公子也會來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很好　我們也想要個繼承人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全力期待一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女婿?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承人?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:08:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說　我…我要成為新娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你　明天儘量展現一下女性魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和行人一組工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後不知不覺進入了好氛圍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就大膽邀請他去草叢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀要努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我努力什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切　變得麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安　凜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴也說有空閒就把她帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.93,0:08:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴很能幹　幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶也說了快到雨天了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要今天完工
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是沒什麼自信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情完全沒做過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.65,0:09:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的　我來教你　交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.30,0:09:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫行人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從凜那裡聽了許多關於你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是凜的母親　理沙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.55,0:09:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是工頭　律
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜的奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.34,0:09:22.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說在這裡工作的都是些態度冷淡的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛　也有一匹奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之　看你還沒習慣現場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜託你做凜的助手好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:35.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜　要好好教他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要手把手親密接觸地教哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.03,0:09:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼　公子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從地基開始教吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.88,0:09:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真擔心那兩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　也是　行人是初學者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴還真是遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人那麼有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們獨處的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會發生什麼事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:11.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　要遲鈍到什麼程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說那傢伙喜歡上姐姐是只是時間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人會喜歡上凜?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得行人對凜　我　炸豬排　乾炸　大家都很喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種喜歡和這個意義完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷戀　愛情　戀愛之心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛之心?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:40.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想到喜歡的人胸中就像被什麼東西填滿一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中像被什麼東西填滿一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連飯都不想吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上就算進被窩也完全睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種喘不過氣來的感覺就是戀愛之心　知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正小鈴現在還不懂這種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那個男人看到了沖澡的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼被感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　行人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正男人都是那幅德行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天要不是被姐姐打飛不知道會變成怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打飛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天要好好地監視跟著他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是發生了什麼就無法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.16,0:11:36.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快點給我來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴這邊就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.72,0:12:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都那麼干脆利落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥們在我出生之前就在這裡工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.56,0:12:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來公子用過錘子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…沒怎麼用過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼　讓我稍微給你見識一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛　公子　好好看著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:43.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是　也有不能看的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜明明不願意被人看裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼平時穿的衣服卻那麼暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子　好好看著呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　凜　沒事吧　凜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又砸到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　都腫起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙又糾纏觸摸姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　真抱歉　公子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美琴　怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀　抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙故意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.73,0:14:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太假惺惺了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦　是誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼　真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　下回再接近姐姐大人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拿更厲害的東西來給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我做好覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:28.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就不能工作了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼難得的好氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這種斜面有點斜的就要輕削一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你做下示範吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子要好好扶住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.71,0:14:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這木工工作還真困難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了　公子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好抓住呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是天然呆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜卻做得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣　就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉　公子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.51,0:15:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強躲過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢　手又滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.41,0:15:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是建房子需要手裡劍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點在公子面前展露一下優點的的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在俘虜之前就會被討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:15:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子　有點弄髒了我先去洗一下臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…凜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.81,0:16:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀　今天還真會手滑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你給我差不多點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為是我找你的碴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣你就不能給我離凜姐遠點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話和我一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的主義可是不為無聊的事情而決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼　害怕身為忍者的我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.67,0:17:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是　要贏我還早100萬年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是絕對不可能的事情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　小鈴很有天賦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回一定要給他看看我的優點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的亂蹦亂跳的　那麼吵在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但多虧兩人的拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房子快造好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.12,0:18:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧　孩子很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比有10年經驗的你做得好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體要散了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你們那麼認真拼命競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家今天辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡情吃喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果優點一個都沒給公子看到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說丟臉的地方倒全被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.43,0:19:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人　辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的很活躍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼活躍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是像笨蛋一樣認真了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上一定會全身肌肉痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　小孩不喝一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:52.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是未成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛　沒什麼好吃的東西別客氣吃喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒做好吃的東西真對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:05.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這是凜做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.87,0:20:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都有做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒　很了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.06,0:20:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.59,0:20:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和凜結婚的話每天都能吃到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木工的水平也那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都非常歡迎來我家做女婿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:51.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的　媽媽在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.56,0:21:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿來好吃的西瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住　畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在親熱什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:38.10,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H579A4F}「雨也是…朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得睡不著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.32,0:23:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這心情　就是美琴所說的那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.95,0:23:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小石頭　咕嚕咕嚕在滾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:22.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.92,0:23:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛之凍魚料理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.65,0:23:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯉魚旗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.48,0:23:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時髦的和服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…個
